    </h1>
    <ul class="hidden md:flex space-x-6">
      <li class="opacity-0">
        <a
          href="#about"
          class="text-foreground border-b-2 border-transparent hover:text-accent hover:border-accent pb-1 transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out"
        >
          About
        </a>
      </li>
      <li class="opacity-0">
        <a
